data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and style in this meticulously maintained 3-bed, 2-bath, all-brick, single level home. Recently updated kitchen and bathrooms add a modern touch, while the expansive fenced in backyard invites relaxation and outdoor enjoyment. Also enjoy the wired storage building in the back for all your DIY projects. A haven of tranquility awaits in this well-crafted residence. Call today for your own private showing!
